Why is FC Road Pune famous?
FC Road Pune: A haven for food, fashion & fun
FC Road is a haven for food enthusiasts, with an abundance of eateries and food stalls. Start your journey with a visit to Vaishali, an iconic restaurant famous for its delectable South Indian dishes and the legendary "Brun Maska." Savour the flavours of crispy dosas, fluffy idlis, and aromatic filter coffee.7 Jul 2023
